<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>내 수강과목 | 학사관리시스템</title>

    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet"
          href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/pretendard/dist/web/static/pretendard.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet"
          href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" />

    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Pretendard', sans-serif; }
    </style>
</head>

<body class="bg-[#F5F7FA] text-gray-800">

{{> studentLayout/studentHeader }}

<main class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-10">

    <!-- 페이지 제목 -->
    <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-6">
        <div>
            <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 flex items-center gap-2">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-bookmark text-blue-600"></i>
                내 수강과목
            </h1>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500">
                현재 학기에 수강 중인 강의 목록입니다. 카드를 클릭하면 각 강의의 홈 화면으로 이동합니다.
            </p>
        </div>

        <a href="/courseListForEnrollment"
           class="hidden md:inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-xl bg-blue-600 text-white text-sm font-medium shadow hover:bg-blue-700 transition">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i>
            수강신청 하러 가기
        </a>
    </div>

    <!-- 수강과목 카드 리스트 -->
    <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-5">

        {{#courseList}}
        <article class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg border border-gray-100 p-5 flex flex-col justify-between cursor-pointer transition"
                 onclick="location.href='/studentCourseHome?courseNo={{courseNo}}'">

            <!-- 상단: 과목 기본 정보 -->
            <div>
                <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3">
                    <div>
                        <p class="text-[11px] font-semibold text-blue-600 mb-1">
                            {{deptName}}
                        </p>
                        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 leading-snug">
                            {{courseName}}
                        </h2>
                        <div class="mt-2 flex flex-wrap gap-3 text-xs text-gray-600">
                            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1">
                                <i class="fa-solid fa-user-tie w-4"></i>
                                {{professorName}} 교수님
                            </span>
                            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1">
                                <i class="fa-solid fa-coins w-4"></i>
                                {{courseScore}} 학점
                            </span>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <span class="inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full text-[11px] font-semibold bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-700">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check mr-1 text-[10px]"></i>
                        수강중
                    </span>
                </div>

                <!-- 수업 시간 -->
                <div class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-600 flex items-center gap-2">
                    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue-50 text-blue-800 text-xs font-medium">
                        <i class="fa-regular fa-calendar-days w-4"></i>
                        <span>{{yoilName}}요일 · {{courseTimeStart}}교시 ~ {{courseTimeEnd}}교시</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </article>
        {{/courseList}}

        {{^courseList}}
        <!-- 수강중인 과목이 없을 때 -->
        <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-2">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-dashed border-gray-300 p-10 text-center text-gray-500">
                <i class="fa-regular fa-circle-question text-3xl text-gray-400 mb-3"></i>
                <p class="text-sm mb-2">현재 수강 중인 과목이 없습니다.</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-4">
                    수강신청 기간이라면 아래 버튼을 눌러 강의를 신청해 보세요.
                </p>
                <a href="/courseListForEnrollment"
                   class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 mt-1 rounded-xl bg-blue-600 text-white text-sm font-medium hover:bg-blue-700">
                    수강신청 하러 가기
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right text-xs"></i>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
        {{/courseList}}

    </section>

</main>

{{> studentLayout/studentFooter }}

</body>
</html>
